text: Hi! I hope you're doing well :sparkles:
Today we had some guest speakers come to my uni today and speak to us about Blue Zoo~ :smile:
It was Will Cook with Marcus Taylor and Mai Atzomon! All Hertfordshire Uni Alumni aha

The  talk was great and afterwards they went round to everyone for showreel crit. I spoke Mai and she was super lovely and she told me that you were on the same team as you aha. And that she also does e-mentoring on prospela.

I'm currently working on my final year film with my group and now that we have a proxy rig, my group and I will be able to start blocking out our shots soon :slightly_smiling_face:
